<h2>Be.Ahead</h2>
<p>Assessment time: 2hrs 30 mins</p>
<p>A lifestyle discussion to help you achieve your goals. </p>
<p>Core tests including blood tests for type 2 diabetes, anaemia and cholesterol; mobility &amp; flexibility review; mental health and wellbeing discussion; self-selected lifestyle module with behaviour change coaching.</p>
<p>Up to 60 mins with a Doctor to talk through health concerns and do additional tests depending on what's clinically appropriate for you as well as having a closer look at mental health.</p>
<p>30 minute in-depth look at your fitness using a Wattbike - an intelligent smart trainer.</p>
<p><strong><em>Please note: in order to keep customers and staff safe, we are unable to see customers who are required to self-isolate or quarantine under UK government guidelines. This includes: customers with symptoms of COVID-19 in the 7 days prior to their appointment; customers who have had contact with a potential/confirmed case (including household members)  of COVID-19 in the 14 days prior to their appointment; and customers who have returned from a country requiring a quarantine period in the 14 days prior to their appointment.</em></strong></p>
</div>
<div class="productNameInfo hidden ada8d32f-43c5-4f20-abcc-48ab5cc81381" data-href="" data-showasoverlay="True">
<h2>Be.Motivated</h2>
<p>Assessment time: 60 minutes</p>
<p>A lifestyle discussion to help you achieve your goals.</p>
<p>Core tests include blood tests for type 2 diabetes and cholesterol; mobility &amp; flexibility review; Mental health and wellbeing discussion; a self-selected lifestyle module with behaviour change coaching.</p>
<p>Please note this assessment does not included dedicated time with a doctor.</p>
<p><strong><em>Please note: in order to keep customers and staff safe, we are unable to see customers who are required to self-isolate or quarantine under UK government guidelines. This includes: customers with symptoms of COVID-19 in the 7 days prior to their appointment; customers who have had contact with a potential/confirmed case (including household members) of COVID-19 in the 14 days prior to their appointment; and customers who have returned from a country requiring a quarantine period in the 14 days prior to their appointment.</em></strong></p>
</div>
<div class="productNameInfo hidden 5e5efe81-febf-4aa5-929f-73a21afd4bcd" data-href="" data-showasoverlay="True">
<h2>Be.Reassured</h2>
<p>Assessment time: 120 minutes </p>
<p>A lifestyle discussion to help you achieve your goals.  </p>
<p>Core tests including blood tests for type 2 diabetes; anaemia and cholesterol; mobility &amp; flexibility review; mental health and wellbeing discussion; self-selected lifestyle module with behaviour change coaching. </p>
<p>Up to 60 minutes with a Dr to talk through health concerns and do additional tests depending on what's clinically appropriate for you as well as having a closer look at mental health - Be.Me app which includes virtual coach Luke who will help you navigate the app, complete health &amp; wellbeing questionnaires, set goals and stay motivated - Two lifestyle coaching calls.</p>
<p><strong><em>Please note: in order to keep customers and staff safe, we are unable to see customers who are required to self-isolate or quarantine under UK government guidelines. This includes: customers with symptoms of COVID-19 in the 7 days prior to their appointment; customers who have had contact with a potential/confirmed case (including household members)  of COVID-19 in the 14 days prior to their appointment; and customers who have returned from a country requiring a quarantine period in the 14 days prior to their appointment.</em></strong></p>
