<div class="productNameInfo hidden df2dab54-491a-466c-98e7-64783a30edd3" data-href="/" data-showasoverlay="True">
<h2>Mature health</h2>
<p>Assessment time: 2 hours</p>
<p>With tests designed specifically for men and women over 65, this assessment can give you a helpful picture of your health in later life. It includes: </p>
<ul class="small-dot-rte">
<li> - A core set of tests that aim to identify key health risks</li>
<li> - Guidance on a healthier lifestyle </li>
<li> - Up to 60 minutes with a doctor including a focused physical examination</li>
<li> - Tests focused on mobility and posture </li>
<li> - Tests for male or female specific cancers </li>
</ul>
<br/>
<p><strong><em>Please note: in order to keep customers and staff safe, we are unable to see customers who are required to self-isolate or quarantine under UK government guidelines. This includes: customers with symptoms of COVID-19 in the 10 days prior to their appointment; customers who have had contact with a potential/confirmed case (including household members) of COVID-19 in the 14 days prior to their appointment; and customers who have returned from a country requiring a quarantine period in the 14 days prior to their appointment.</em></strong></p>
