<p class="popup-content">Our short GP appointments for adults over 18 years old are available daily at our clinics across the country.
We would recommend this length of appointment if you meet any of the following:
You have one concern or minor illness to discuss with the doctor or require a repeat prescription for non controlled drugs.
</p>
<p class="popup-content">These short appointments are generally not recommended for where you have more than one issue to discuss or have an existing complex medical history (Please see information on 30 min standard appointment)
</p>
<p>If the purpose of the appointment is for a cervical smear or prostate test, please contact the bookings team directly</p>
<p>If despite booking a short appointment, more time is required, weâ€™ll endeavour to make this available to you. Extra time is only available in 15 minute or 30 minute intervals and there will be a charge for this.</p>
