<h2>Menopause Plan Initial Appointment</h2>
<p>This appointment is primarily designed for individuals who feel that they are suffering from the menopause or wish to discuss the menopause in more detail with one of our specialised trained GPâ€™s</p>
<p>As part of your plan you will receive an initial telephone appointment with one of our Menopause GPâ€™s which may last up to 45min depending upon your requirements. The GP will then guide you through any next steps if necessary, which can include them providing you with a private prescription or a referral on to further care. The GP will provide you with a personalised care plan. You will also get a 15min telephone follow up appointment at 12 weeks which you will need to call Bupa to arrange.</p>
<p>In addition, you will be given a whole yearâ€™s access to our team of menopause trained nurses on our 24/7 Bupa Anytime HealthLine.</p>
