<h2 class="popup-title">Musculoskeletal services</h2>
<p class="popup-content">Our musculoskeletal physicians are experienced in diagnosing problems with muscles, bones and joints, helping you return to normal activity as soon as possible. This includes issues ranging from acute back pain, sprains, muscle tears and sporting injuries.</p>
<p class="popup-content">Book an initial consultation at one of our health centres and our physicians will be able to recommend treatment to help guide you back to your best. </p>
<h1 class="popup-title">Physiotherapy</h1>
<p class="popup-content">Physiotherapy can help reduce physical discomfort, improve movement and strengthen and rehabilitate specific areas of your body. Our physiotherapy services are available to everyone aged 18 and over, even if you donâ€™t have Bupa health insurance.</p>
<p class="popup-content">Our physiotherapists provide a range of treatments across many of our health centres, such as joint mobilisation, manual therapy, massage, acupuncture and even shockwave therapy for the treatment of chronic pain.</p>
